Package com.github.leanfe.api

Class LoadManager

java.lang.Object
com.github.leanfe.api.LoadManager
public class LoadManager extends Object
A manager class that loads DLL and JAR files. This is a class that contains functions and mechanisms for loading DLL and .JAD files required for Minecraft.
Since:
1.0

      public void load​(String dllPath, String pathJar, String minecraftJar) throws IOException, AgentException
      The method for load all DLL and .jar files needed for start a minecraft.
      Parameters:
      dllPath - The path to all .dll files for minecraft.
